column5: Hey gang! I am curious if the Credit is open water and fishable right now.  Im thinking about heading there on Sunday but I would prefer not to drive the couple of hours to find it high and unfishable.  Not looking for fishing advice, just conditions!  Thanks guys.
Blown wide open, needs another week maybe
Blown wide open, needs another week maybe
I tried to post a pic of water conditions as of Sunday but I dont know how to make it small enough!  Sorry!
Dave, the forums should auto shrink it for you
Crap..... Oh well.  I guess I will wait for another weekend at this point then.  Too bad.
I forgot to say thanks for the info!  I really appreciate it.
Anyone else feel like chocolate milk right now?
DUDE, That's Prime!!!!!!! Bust out the grapefruit sized bags and have ar 'er!!!
I think live minnows or single eggs will be the ticket for that river this weekend
jigs. big monster jigs.  Like bass flippin jigs...with pork trailers
